{"tid":209654,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過拍緊拖鐘意咗另一個","createTime":"2017-04-20T11:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T02:28:18.000Z","uid":17633,"like":5,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b731fc701e8b80722de05e06c5bf423faecd18f0","tid":209654,"uid":17633,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:13:17.000Z","msg":"雖然呢排同現任有啲淡...但我冇諗過要背叛佢<br />\n但係鐘意嘅感覺好難去控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好自然見到佢會心跳 臉紅 一見到佢就會好開心...<br />\n呢啲係咪新鮮感？我忍過咗個感覺係咪就會咁冇咁強烈...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d8eeb9df908f62d5b387951095db7c559f7354","tid":209654,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:14:33.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"bc90bd83e6cd58d162fe75c81a6dd3f27553f05f","tid":209654,"uid":31705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:58:37.000Z","msg":"你未玩夠"},{"pid":"2e99dd3d7dd87b49302f3161184ce4a693b5f9e0","tid":209654,"uid":41703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:00:17.000Z","msg":"我屌你！ 未玩夠唔好拍拖害人！"},{"pid":"11b8af987b4f308220c87ffe66c8c81f4a9980e3","tid":209654,"uid":74532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:05:53.000Z","msg":"小心有報應"},{"pid":"a28a8eb6e366f2a55539449659c9f47e7bcbc0af","tid":209654,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:06:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屌你！ 未玩夠唔好拍拖害人！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"beae169911c8d38328421ff7921545adc851bff2","tid":209654,"uid":24802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:47:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屌你！ 未玩夠唔好拍拖害人！</blockquote><br />\nc打佢真係同左個個女仔一齊？"},{"pid":"78dabf91bd6811914d924fdae9090255ad7c1d80","tid":209654,"uid":72816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:50:36.000Z","msg":"會惹來惡果"},{"pid":"d1391604c10dc6523a7bde0aa1442ac37afe82d3","tid":209654,"uid":17633,"like":1,"disli